This folder contains the necessary files to create spherical caps of ice.
The folder  cut_water_cap/ contains the python script to create the spherical cap.

Type 

    "python cut_water_cap/cut_cap_slab.py -h"

for help


An example to create a hemispherical cap of ih001 with 1nm radius would be:

    "python cut_water_cap/cut_water_cap.py -i ih001/ice.gro -x 3 -y 3 -z 0 -r 1 "

There will be two output files, cut2.gro will be the ice configuration and cut1.gro will be the rest of the SOL molecules
